@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Companies Help - SM Export";
}

<div class="container mt-4">
    <h1>Companies: SM Export</h1>
    <p class="text-muted">Explains the SM Export action on the Companies page.</p>

    <div class="alert alert-info">
        This feature exports company contact and profile fields in CSV format for SurveyMonkey-style use.
    </div>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">What it exports</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Email</li>
        <li>FirstName</li>
        <li>LastName</li>
        <li>CompanyName</li>
        <li>ExternalId</li>
        <li>CompanyDescription</li>
        <li>LastTIN200Year</li>
        <li>FYE2025</li>
        <li>FYE2024</li>
        <li>FYE2023</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">How it is used</h2>
    <p>This export is intended for outbound survey/contact workflows where a CSV file with contact and company fields is required.</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">Filtering</h2>
    <p>If you apply a Last TIN200 Year filter first, only the filtered company set is exported.</p>

    <h2 class="h5 mt-4">File format</h2>
    <p>The file is downloaded as a timestamped <strong>.csv</strong> file.</p>
</div>